Conjure Elemental

This spell allows the druid to request aid from Gaea, in
the form of an elemental servant.  The elemental will
freely serve for one hour, and is capable of assisting
in combat.  These elementals are also empowered to
fly through the skies, following the druid.  An air or
earth elemental may be summoned at mastery level one,
water at level two, and fire at level three; further
levels of mastery also increase the power of the
elemental.  See 'dhelp elemental' for more information.

Command: conjure <air|earth|fire|water>
Base Cost: 150 SP
Base Recovery: slow
Base Effect: follower
Base Duration: one hour (or until logoff)
Guild Level: 26
